history.content:
Hi all,

I am currently seeking interviewees for a Sociology research project I am doing on the work culture of Silicon Valley. 

I am currently recruiting from two subpopulations: 

(a) software engineers who work at Silicon Valley startups

(b) software engineers who work at Silicon Valley big tech companies (e.g. Apple, Meta, Google)

If anyone knows people or has experience at these companies and would be willing to chat with me for a few minutes, it would be greatly appreciated. 

Thank you!

Amanda
